These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, bike, skateboard, car, roller, boat
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, fanta, mirinda, almond-milk, sprite, water
 1. the person drinking water is the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
 6. the person driving the scooter is not the person drinking tea##6
 7. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking tea##7
10. the person drinking tea is the person driving the roller##1
11. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
12. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking water##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
14. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
15. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
16. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
17. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
18. the person driving the boat is the person drinking fanta##1
19. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
20. the person driving the skateboard is not the person drinking sprite##6
21. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
22. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Transport           | roller | bike | boat | helicopter  | car  | skateboard | scooter    |
| Beverage   | tea   | hot-chocolate   | fanta   | mirinda | almond-milk | water        | sprite |

